      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hiya! I&amp;rsquo;m Rich, I do cyber security stuff (for about 20 years at this point). Day to day that tends to include a range of activities around leadership and risk management although i&amp;rsquo;m most happy when knee deep in a debugger or decompiler. Sadly, that doesn&amp;rsquo;t happen as much these days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve managed teams as small as 2 and larger than 100 across various different types of roles and always made it a case to never to lose my technical hands-on abilities. I&amp;rsquo;m a big fan of the &lt;a href=&#34;http://blog.idonethis.com/two-pizza-team/&#34;&gt;two pizza box rule&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I enjoy taking complex problems and producing eloquent solutions; love a good CTF, and who&amp;rsquo;s not playing with AI at this point as well!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;things-about-me&#34;&gt;Things about me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As far as pronouns go, I prefer he/him.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m a big fan of minimalistic design, hence this site&amp;rsquo;s simple design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If i&amp;rsquo;m not at a computer, i&amp;rsquo;m either in, or dreaming about, being underwater or in the mountains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I also dream of one day, taking better photos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m based on the South Coast of the UK.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
